a Tag with sharks.\n\nThe VR controls are super responsive (it feels like a human-shark mind meld): simply look where you want the shark to swim. Pull the trigger to move forward, press the grip button to chomp/eat things.", "short_description": "Eat your friends in 'SHARKS' a cross-platform (PC and VR) multiplayer hunting game. Hunt with groups of up to 10 people online. Eat whatever you can to survive and avoid the zombie sharks: last player standing wins. It's like Gorilla Tag with sharks."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://ezone.com/privacy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Ezone PTY LTD", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://ezone.com/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "459781504968480"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER", "MULTI_USER", "CO_OP"], "id": "219944073774624"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 2, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "245104471462418"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1006562187377203"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "245104471462418"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1720481722, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "245104471462418"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "28597293059857752", "version": "0.1"}, "id": "601272338109301", "channel_name": "LIVE"}]}, "is_for_oculus_keys_only": false, "primary_binaries": {"nodes": [{"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "9571468216200189", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "28597293059857752"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "601272338109301"}]}, "change_log": "Release Notes - v0.1.13 - \"PLAY WITH FRIENDS\"\n\nNow you can invite friends to play with you in SHARKS right from your Quest headset. Just open the main Meta/Oculus menu from within the game, select a friend from the people menu and 'Invite to your location' so you can play and chat in SHARKS together.\n\nFixes:\n- Play with friends fix\n\nDon't forget to collect your free gift from us - a special limited edition Elf Hat (while supplies last). If you love playing SHARKS then buy some skins to show your support. All proceeds from skins go right back into the game: new game modes, customizable items, maps, interactable creatures and objects and multiplayer servers.\n\nThanks so much for playing and please tell your friends: word of mouth is the best way to get more players in the game!\n\nIf you have any feedback or comments, please come chat in the Discord (https://ezone.com/discord). Cheers!\n\n- Simon and Jamie", "created_date": 1733280426, "id": "28597293059857752", "version": "0.1", "version_code": 14, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "9571468216200189", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "28597293059857752"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "601272338109301"}]}, "change_log": "Release Notes - v0.1.13 - \"GIFT GIVING SEASON\"\n\nJust in time for the gift giving season we've added PRIZE CODES to SHARKS. Now you can get prize codes from our Discord (and #sharks on your socials) to unlock packs of goldfish plus rare skins and items.\n\nNew:\n\n- Prize codes: check our Discord and #sharks on your socials for free prizes (try GOLD50)\n- Limited edition skin: SANTA SUIT\n- More Leaderboards: Shark Kills, plus Goldfish, Crabs and Dead Fish Eaten \n\nFixes:\n- Fixed shark colliders with biteable objects\n- Speed limit on thrown objects\n- Meta Destinations fix\n\nDon't forget to collect your free gift from us - a special limited edition Elf Hat (while supplies last). If you love playing SHARKS then buy some skins to show your support. All proceeds from skins go right back into the game: new game modes, customizable items, maps, interactable creatures and objects and multiplayer servers.\n\nThanks so much for playing and please tell your friends: word of mouth is the best way to get more players in the game!\n\nIf you have any feedback or comments, please come chat in the Discord (https://ezone.com/discord). Cheers!\n\n- Simon and Jamie", "created_date": 1733211861, "id": "28589259190661139", "version": "0.1", "version_code": 13, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "9571468216200189", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "28597293059857752"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "601272338109301"}]}, "change_log": "Release Notes - v0.1.12 - \"EXPLOSIONS AND ELF HATS\"\n\nWe've reworked the physics so now you can have even more fun with cannonballs and exploding air tanks. Create traps and set off chain reactions to slowdown other sharks. And while you're exploding other sharks get into the holiday spirit with a free gift from us - a special limited edition Elf Hat!\n\nNew:\n- Free Elf Hat (for a limited time!)\n- Scuba tank now a biteable and throwable bomb\n- Explosions cause chain reactions\n- Moveable items react to explosions\n- More diver Dad jokes\n- Above ocean elements (see if you can access them!)\n\nFixes:\n- Damage caused by explosions proportional to distance\n- Skins purchased outside the game are auto-activated \n- Players outside the map fix\n- Tweaked goldfish rewards\n- Multiplayer updated (so make sure you're friends update too so you can play on the same servers)\n\nIf you love playing SHARKS then get the GOLD Founders Skin to show your support. All proceeds from skins go right back into the game: new game modes, customizable items, maps, interactable creatures and objects and multiplayer servers.\n\nThanks so much for playing and please tell your friends: word of mouth is the best way to get more players in the game!\n\nIf you have any feedback or comments, please come chat in the Discord (https://ezone.com/discord). Cheers!\n\n- Simon and Jamie", "created_date": 1732697605, "id": "28531348619785530", "version": "0.1", "version_code": 12, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "9571468216200189", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "28597293059857752"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "601272338109301"}]}, "change_log": "Release Notes - v0.1l - \"FOUNDERS SKIN\"\n\nIn this release we've added an exclusive limited edition FOUNDERS SKIN for the Meta Quest that turns your shark into a solid gold shiny beast.\n\nIf you love playing SHARKS then get this skin to show your support. All proceeds go right back into the game: new game modes, customizable items, maps, interactable creatures and objects and multiplayer servers.\n\nNew:\n- Gold Founders Skin for Meta Quest\n- Win reward: goldfish spawned near leaderboard - the more you win, the more you get!\n- Stats: kills, bites, wins, eaten objects + more\n- Online leaderboards and achievements\n- Updated menus\n- Improved unlocked chest graphics\n\nFixes:\n- Multiplayer: game round start bug fix\n- Rocket powerup more responsive\n- More accurate online player count\n- Improved fade-in-out between scenes\n- Increased health from eating some fish", "created_date": 1732179687, "id": "28470653645855028", "version": "0.1", "version_code": 11, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "9571468216200189", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "28597293059857752"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "601272338109301"}]}, "change_log": "Release Notes - v0.1k - \"HEALTH UI\"\n\nIn this release we've added onscreen health UI so you can see how much damage you are causing and how much health you receive for food.\n\n- Health UI\n- HUD always active\n\nFixes:\n- Removed HUD toggle from settings\n\nAs we get further along we'll be looking for more feedback regarding gameplay, etc, but for now we just want to make sure everyone can get started and that the multiplayer is solid. If you have any feedback or comments, please direct them to the Discord. Cheers!\n\n- Simon and Jamie", "created_date": 1717484016, "id": "26440873605499719", "version": "0.1", "version_code": 10, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}]}}, "viewer": {"user": null}}}